{"tid":1650071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國務卿蓬佩奧以反烏托邦小說《1984》 比喻中共在新疆拘禁過百萬名穆斯林","createTime":"2019-10-12T20:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T20:16:17.000Z","uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed101555cc57d3eaf5b99ed8eda1d93b10857bf6","tid":1650071,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:14:01.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧在田納西州出席一個活動時，以小說《1984》來比喻中國新疆的狀況。蓬佩奧指中共在新疆，拘禁了超過一百萬名穆斯林，並在營房內侵犯他們的權利。蓬佩奧又表示，希望正受到中國壓力的NBA，能夠體察新疆的境況。<br />\n<br />\n《1984》在1949年出版，是英國小說家奧威爾的作品，書中以「老大哥」來隱喻控制一切的極權政府，藉此描述個人自由及思想遭到剝奪及壓制。由於當時蘇聯的斯太林大肆肅清異己，外界因而相信，這本書是影射共產黨管治下的社會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191012/60144742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60144742&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGeoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=d7c687bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60144742&h=7fe02354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191012/60144742</a>"},{"pid":"f66bde30266b5781c73535f192a428145ca94c74","tid":1650071,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdsguU2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdsguU2.jpg&h=ae3e60b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>10.13 10.14 不見不散</strong></span></span>"}]}